                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L1 21h22M12 6l7.5 13h-15M11 10h2v4h-2M11 16h2v2h-2"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Google Update</span>
